        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.4</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2025 17:57:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.4</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.0.4</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Removed hardcoded developer credentials from repository</li>
                    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Build system now uses environment variables for signing</li>
                    <li><strong>Developer:</strong> Added comprehensive developer setup documentation</li>
                    <li><strong>Build:</strong> Repository is now safe for public sharing</li>
                    <li>GitHub Actions continues to build unsigned releases automatically</li>
                </ul>
                <p>This is a security-focused release that removes sensitive developer credentials from the codebase while maintaining full functionality.</p>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
